request.description:
### Mark Attendance

This endpoint is used to mark attendance for an event.

#### Request

- Method: POST

- Endpoint: `{{BASE_URL}}/mark-attendance`

- Body:
    - event_place (string, required): The place where the event took place.

    - event_date (string, required): The date of the event.


#### Response

The response for this request can be represented as a JSON schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {
          "type": "integer"
        },
        "opus_pc_id": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "event_place": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "event_date": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

